<section id="services-1188">
    <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-content">
            <span class="cs-topper">What's Included</span>
            <h2 class="cs-title">Everything's Already in There</h2>
            <p class="cs-text">
                Everything listed below comes standard. No premium tiers or unlocking features later.
            </p>
        </div>
        <ul class="cs-card-group">
            <li class="cs-item">
                <picture class="cs-picture">
                    <img class="cs-icon"
                            src="/assets/svgs/tick-small.svg"
                            loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="icon" width="33" height="38" aria-hidden="true">
                </picture>
                <!-- Text Grouped For Flexbox-->
                <div class="cs-text-group">
                    <h3 class="cs-h3">Automatic Reminders</h3>
                    <p class="cs-item-text">Text and email reminders go out before every appointment without you doing anything. People forget they booked things all the time. This fixes that.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <picture class="cs-picture">
                    <img class="cs-icon" src="/assets/svgs/tick-small.svg"
                            loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="icon" width="33" height="38" aria-hidden="true">
                </picture>
                <!-- Text Grouped For Flexbox-->
                <div class="cs-text-group">
                    <h3 class="cs-h3">Deposits and Payments</h3>
                    <p class="cs-item-text">If you want to take payment upfront, you can. Card payments are processed securely. People are much less likely to cancel when they've already paid something.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <picture class="cs-picture">
                    <img class="cs-icon"
                            src="/assets/svgs/tick-small.svg"
                            loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="icon" width="33" height="38" aria-hidden="true">
                </picture>
                <!-- Text Grouped For Flexbox-->
                <div class="cs-text-group">
                    <h3 class="cs-h3">Syncs With Your Calendar</h3>
                    <p class="cs-item-text">Works with Google Calendar, Apple, Outlook - whatever you already use. New bookings show up on your phone automatically. You don't have to check two different places or accidentally double-book yourself.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <picture class="cs-picture">
                    <img class="cs-icon"
                            src="/assets/svgs/tick-small.svg" loading="lazy"
                            decoding="async" alt="icon" width="33" height="38" aria-hidden="true">
                </picture>
                <!-- Text Grouped For Flexbox-->
                <div class="cs-text-group">
                    <h3 class="cs-h3">Multiple Therapists</h3>
                    <p class="cs-item-text">If you've got a team, each person gets their own schedule. Customers can pick who they want when they book. This keeps everything organised as you grow.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
                <picture class="cs-picture">
                    <img class="cs-icon"
                            src="/assets/svgs/tick-small.svg" loading="lazy"
                            decoding="async" alt="icon" width="33" height="38" aria-hidden="true">
                </picture>
                <!-- Text Grouped For Flexbox-->
                <div class="cs-text-group">
                    <h3 class="cs-h3">Your Rules</h3>
                    <p class="cs-item-text">You set the boundaries. How much notice you need, gaps between appointments, days you don't work. The system follows whatever rules make sense for how you run things.</p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
                                

                              
